revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
{{Lua|Module:Suppress categories}}
{{Template shortcut|strip categories|suppresscats|stripcats|supcat}}
<!-- Categories go at the bottom of this page and interwikis go in Wikidata. -->

This template strips [[Help:Category|categories]] from [[Help:Wiki markup|wikitext]]. For example, if passed the code "<code><nowiki>foo[[Category:Some category]]</nowiki></code>", it will return only "<code>foo</code>". It can be used to strip categories from templates as well; if passed the code "<code><nowiki>{{my template}}</nowiki></code>", it will return the template output minus the categories.

The template properly handles categories escaped with the [[Help:Colon trick|colon trick]], categories whose names include invalid characters such as "<code>></code>", and categories that are surrounded with [[WP:NOWIKI|nowiki]] tags. However, it does not support complex wikitext such as nested links or [[WP:MAGIC|magic words]] like <code><nowiki>__TOC__</nowiki></code>. Even so, it should still remove the vast majority of categories from any given wikitext.

== Usage ==

<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{suppress categories|''input text''}}</syntaxhighlight>

== Examples ==

{| class="wikitable"
! Code
! Output
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Some category]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Some category]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Some category]]bar[[Category:Another category]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Some category]]bar[[Category:Another category]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo{{{some_parameter|[[Category:Bar]]}}}}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo{{{some_parameter|[[Category:Bar]]}}}}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Bad ca[]tegory link]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Bad ca[]tegory link]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[:Category:Colon trick]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[:Category:Colon trick]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Piped link|bar]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Piped link|bar]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Piped link|ba[]r]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[Category:Piped link|ba[]r]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[non-category link]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[non-category link]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|foo[[ Category : Some category with spaces ]]}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|foo[[ Category : Some category with spaces ]]}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{suppress categories|{{User alternative account name|Example}}}}</nowiki></code>
| {{suppress categories|{{User alternative account name|Example}}}}
|-
|}

== See also ==

* [[Wikipedia:Category suppression]]
* {{tl|Draft categories}}

